# Packet-Level Tao Distinctness Does Not Clear Step-011 Without A Theorem-Facing One-Sided Gain

Status: `VERIFIED` Step-011 prior-art verdict with `INFERRED` label-order
diagnosis

The Step-011 prior-art screen does not reduce the coupled energy-helicity
branch to pure repackaging, but it still does not produce a Step-2-worthy
distinct theorem-facing gain.

The narrow distinct element that survives is exact-NS-specific:
packet-complete helical-triad rigidity with mandatory conjugate completion and
unavoidable spectator couplings, used as a Tao discriminator against averaged
or shell-style freedoms.

That surviving discriminator matters only in a limited way. It shows the
branch is not merely recycled same-helicity folklore, Waleffe-style triad
language, helical-decimation optimism, or shell intuition under a new label.

But the same record still fails to show one theorem-facing one-sided gain on
the declared stretching or enstrophy burden, and it still lacks a frozen
baseline cash-out and same-currency minimum threshold for the later coercivity
gate.

So the honest Step-011 filing remains:
`setup obstruction, branch should stop before coercivity gate`,
with calibration obstruction and prior-art-adjacent noncoercivity recorded as
supporting reasons rather than as a rescue or a stronger primary label.

