+- what gain is already standard;
+- what exact new gain this branch claims beyond that baseline;
+- and why that gain survives stopping, filtration, localization, and
+  import debt.
+
+So the honest filing is obstruction rather than survival:
+prior-art and anti-repackaging obstruction is already active on the stochastic
+record, and the branch should stop before further formal identity work.
